title: The Biggest Fantasy Fallers From the Offseason | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
This offseason has been tough for many players, Aaron Rodgers being one. We highlight the fantasy players whose 2020 outlook took the biggest hit after free agency and the NFL draft. 
Host: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
